- RevenueCat or store billing APIs
- Other comparable providers

Third parties may process data under their own privacy policies. Please review those policies for details.

## 7. Advertising and Analytics

Some apps may show ads or use analytics tools. These tools may use device identifiers, cookies, or similar technologies to deliver and measure content and ads.

Where required by law, we request consent before enabling personalized ads or non-essential analytics. You can change preferences in app/device settings when available.

## 8. Data Retention

We keep personal data only as long as needed for the purposes in this policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law. Retention periods depend on data type, legal obligations, and business needs.

## 9. Data Security

We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational safeguards designed to protect your information. No method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

## 10. International Data Transfers

Your information may be processed in countries other than your own. Where required, we use lawful transfer mechanisms and safeguards for cross-border data transfers.

